| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7451 — Recovery Inhibition (blacksuit)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 99fa7fe0-8776-5659-af78-d9b8b5bed355"
